Selenium Web Driver - is a collection of open course APIs which are used to automate the testing of a web application.
Selenium Web Driver tool is used to automate web application testing to verify that it works as expected. 
It support many browsers such as FireFox, Chrome, IE, and Safari
Web Driver is an API. It is written more than one language which and they are called language bindings. 
The API has functions to controll a browser. You use the functions in writing a script that controls the browser in the way you want.
